sequenceDiagram
    participant Autor
    participant API as API de publicación
    participant Classifier as Clasificador de autor
    participant Queue as Cola de fan-out
    participant Worker as Fan-out worker
    participant Timeline as Timeline materializado
    participant Reader as Timeline reader
    participant Rank as Ranking simple

    Autor->>API: publicar(tweet)
    API->>Classifier: medir alcance
    alt autor normal
        Classifier->>Queue: fan-out job
        Queue->>Worker: procesar seguidores
        Worker->>Timeline: escribir entradas
    else autor de alto alcance
        Classifier-->>API: guardar solo por autor
    end

    Reader->>Timeline: leer entradas materializadas
    Reader->>Reader: mezclar autores de alto alcance
    Reader->>Rank: ordenar candidatos
    Rank-->>Reader: timeline
